---

---

<section
  id="about"
  class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-slate-800/80 text-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="fade-in-section max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-teal-400">
          About Me
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          My name is Matt Vincent Magadaro. I am studying Information Technology
          at the University of San Carlos and am currently getting my Bachelor's
          degree. I've been curious about computers my whole life, and after 4
          years, I have become well-versed in coding.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          When I am not coding, I like to spend time doing my hobbies whether
          that is gaming or going to the gym. I am also always keen to learn
          more about the tech world.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center">
        <div
          class="relative w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-slate-700 shadow-2xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300 bg-slate-700"
        >
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/images/profile.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <img
              src="/images/profile.jpg"
              alt="Matt Vincent Magadaro"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-[center_30%]"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
